</span></div><p itemprop="description">这只镜头我前前后后用了将近1年，下面是18/23/35/55这四组常用焦段的照片：</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgxvwp/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/15/5f37db91ed3405160.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="XT1+XF1855（18mm）"/></a>XT1+XF1855（18mm）</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgxvwp/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/15/5f37db87074999194.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="XT1+XF1855（23mm）轻微后期+裁剪"/></a>XT1+XF1855（23mm）轻微后期+裁剪</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="J_selected_delete"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgxvwp/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/15/5f37db87410d16585.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="XT2+XF1855（35mm）后期"/></a>XT2+XF1855（35mm）后期</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgxvwp/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/15/5f37db89cd4d68343.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="XT1+XF1855（35mm）无后期"/></a>XT1+XF1855（35mm）无后期</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgxvwp/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/15/5f37db901e0189100.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="XT2+XF1855（18mm）后期"/></a>XT2+XF1855（18mm）后期</span></p><p itemprop="description">这支镜头最大的特点就是没有特点。18mm的广角端够用吗？够用，但是总是还想着16或是更广的焦段；55mm的长焦端够用吗？够用，但55mm端的最大光圈只有f4，拍起糖水片来会力不从心。</p><p itemprop="description">于是在综合了需求和预算之后，我又添加了第二支镜头：XF60f 2.4 Macro。</p><h2 id="cl_2">XF60 Macro</h2>
